ble to follow every step of your delivery, from the preparation of your order until it arrives at your doorstep.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Thanks to this major improvement, you will no longer be uncertain about the arrival time of your meal. Once your order is on its way, you will receive real-time notifications, informing you of the progress of your delivery. You will know exactly when the delivery person is on his way to your address and accurately estimate the remaining waiting time.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>This real-time tracking provides extra peace of mind, especially on busy days when every minute counts. This will allow you to better plan your schedule and be ready to welcome your freshly prepared meal as soon as it arrives at your doorstep.</p><p><br></p><p>We are constantly striving to improve our delivery service to give you the best possible experience. Real-time delivery tracking is one of the many new features we\'ve introduced to make your ordering experience even more enjoyable.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Stay connected with us for more exciting improvements to come. We are delighted to continue to offer you convenient, reliable and ever more sophisticated food delivery services to satisfy your taste buds and make your daily life easier.</p>','','2023-06-07 15:02:50','2023-06-07 15:02:50','2023-06-30 08:00:00',0,0,1,NULL,2,5),(157,'Expérience utilisateur améliorée avec une base plus solide','<p>Nous sommes heureux de vous présenter les dernières améliorations apportées à notre site de livraison de nourriture, qui se traduisent par une expérience utilisateur améliorée et une base plus solide.</p><p><br></p><p>Nous avons consacré du temps et des efforts considérables pour renforcer la stabilité de notre plateforme. Ainsi, vous pourrez profiter d\'une expérience fluide et sans interruption lors de votre navigation sur notre site. Fini les chargements lents des pages ou les erreurs imprévues qui peuvent gâcher votre plaisir de commander vos plats 