ner restaurants to offer you the best deals and guarantee the quality of the meals offered. We ensure that each promotion is carefully selected to provide you with an exceptional dining experience at a great price.</p><p><br></p><p>To not miss any of our exclusive promotions, be sure to subscribe to our newsletter and follow our social networks. We will keep you informed of all special offers, promo codes and upcoming events. You will be able to take full advantage of our promotions and save on your orders.</p><p><br></p><p>We pride ourselves on being able to offer you attractive promotions that add extra value to your ordering experience with us. Our goal is to offer you tasty meals at great prices, while maintaining the quality and freshness of our ingredients.</p><p><br></p><p>Take advantage of our exclusive promotions now and discover new flavors at an advantageous price. Whether you\'re ordering for yourself, your family or for a special event, our promotions allow you to enjoy delicious meals while saving money.</p><p><br></p><p>Don\'t forget to check our website and our communication channels regularly to make sure you don\'t miss any special offers. We are here to offer you exceptional promotions and unique culinary experiences. Contact us if you have any questions or special requests. Your satisfaction is our top priority and we are here to serve you.</p>','','2023-06-07 15:46:38','2023-06-07 15:46:38','2023-06-03 08:00:00',0,0,1,40,2,9),(165,'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet','Laoreet suspendisse interdum consectetur libero id faucibus nisl tincidunt. Magna ac placerat vestibulum lectus mauris ultrices. Varius sit amet mattis vulputate. Vitae tortor condimentum lacinia quis vel eros donec. Et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis. Sodales ut etiam sit amet. Massa massa ultricies mi quis hendrerit dolor magna eget. Massa tincidunt dui ut ornare lectus sit amet. Amet aliquam id diam maecenas ultricies mi eget. Aliquet bibendum enim facilisis gravida neque convallis a